<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-09-01T09:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-09-01T09:00:00-05:00" n="1145" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1145">
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Italy</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_PTN1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Page</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the</hi>
                            <gloss type="to">
                                <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State</hi>
                            </gloss>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Rome</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-09-01T15:00:00+01:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">September 1, 1915, 3 p. m.</hi>
                                </date>
                                <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 9.25 p. m.</hi>]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>385. Your August 30, 5 p. m., received from Berne. Italian Government
                            last autumn placed embargo on arms and ammunition with other commodities
                            simply because they were needed for Italy herself. They recognize right
                            under Hague convention to sell arms to belligerents.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="#p_PTN1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Nelson Page</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>